@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v2 + 0.36 + tmp + 0.80)))
    v2 = v0
    v2 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.62 / v2 + 0.99)) - 0.37)
    v0 = wp.sin(0.08)
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.88) - wp.exp(v2 + 0.44)) / wp.abs((v2 + 0.28 + v0 + 0.53)))
    v1 = 0.46
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin(v1))
    v2 = wp.exp(v2)
    data[tid] = v0
